photograph of herself. It is sweet. but too old looking - 
I wish you would have your picture taken for me - just a little one, and maybe you and Amama would have one taken together - that would be so wonderful - I don't mean an expensive one! There used to be places where you could have postcard pictures taken in New York - while you wait! 
Did you see teh article in the March Cosmopolitan? quoting Bob Davis as sook, 

