along with other men of note who claim to know more about cooking than women!- You should read it -also the story by "Pearls. Buck" in the same issue: it is worth while, you should read it dear. 
Be a good girl, kiss Amama for me, and find out. about illumination and em-broidery soon - Love, loads of it, 
your old Mother. 